					<p class="grid__item-description">The Somali language is a rich and complex tongue spoken by millions of people in the Horn of Africa and around the world. Yet, for too long, it has been underserved by the digital age, with few resources and tools available for Somalis to use and develop their language online. That is why we at Kumi LLC are proud to introduce our new project, the Brainchild, a tech revolution in digitalizing the Somali language model.</p>
