					<p class="grid__item-description">The Brainchild is a groundbreaking effort to create a comprehensive and accessible digital platform for the Somali language, from speech recognition to machine translation to natural language processing. We believe that by investing in the development of the Somali language, we can empower Somalis to connect with each other and the wider world, unlock new opportunities for education and economic development, and preserve and enrich their culture for generations to come..</p>
